--daily summary
SELECT
    fact_renovaciones_integrado_key ,
    src_sys_cd ,
    policy_num ,
    policy_item_num ,
    policy_item_id ,
    policy_status_desc ,
    policy_eff_dt ,
    policy_exp_dt ,
    policy_issue_dt ,
    acct_mth ,
    acct_yr ,
    agreement ,
    coins_type_cd ,
    policy_curr_cd ,
    dim_branch_office_key ,
    dim_broker_key ,
    dim_insured_key ,
    dim_lob_key ,
    dim_policyholder_key ,
    dim_prd_pln_hrchy_key ,
    facult_prem_amt ,
    facult_ind ,
    fleet_ind ,
    broker_comm_amt ,
    gwp_amt ,
    rec_crt_dtm ,
    rec_updt_dtm ,
    actv_rec_ind ,
    etl_audit_id ,
    document_type ,
    sales_type ,
    valid_ind ,
    affects_direct_premium_amt ,
    exempt_direct_premium_amt ,
    new_direct_premium_amt ,
    renewal_direct_premium_amt ,
    endorsement_direct_premium_amt,
    next_policy ,
    previous_policy ,
    item_renovated_ind ,
    cycle_number ,
    cycle_state ,
    renovation_type ,
    plate_number ,
    insured_rut_num ,
    policyholder_rut_num ,
    Lob_mkt_ref_code ,
    mv_id ,
    mv_reason_cd ,
    mv_reason_desc ,
    branch_office_name,
    broker_name ,
    insured_name ,
    lob_desc ,
    policyholder_name ,
    prd_desc ,
    broker_rut_num ,
    lob_cd ,
    pln_cd ,
    address_desc_insured,
    comuna_name_insured,
    region_name_insured,
    address_desc_policyholder,
    comuna_name_policyholder,
    region_name_policyholder,
    coaseguro
FROM
    (
        SELECT
            fact.fact_renovaciones_integrado_key ,
            fact.src_sys_cd ,
            fact.policy_num ,
            fact.policy_item_num,
            fact.policy_item_id ,
            fact.policy_status_desc ,
            fact.policy_eff_dt ,
            fact.policy_exp_dt ,
            fact.policy_issue_dt ,
            fact.acct_mth ,
            fact.acct_yr ,
            fact.agreement ,
            fact.coins_type_cd ,
            fact.policy_curr_cd ,
            fact.dim_branch_office_key ,
            fact.dim_broker_key ,
            fact.dim_insured_key ,
            fact.dim_lob_key ,
            fact.dim_policyholder_key ,
            fact.dim_prd_pln_hrchy_key ,
            fact.facult_prem_amt ,
            fact.facult_ind ,
            fact.fleet_ind ,
            (fact.broker_comm_amt * c.uf_lcl_curr_clsng_val ) AS broker_comm_amt,
            (fact.gwp_amt * c.uf_lcl_curr_clsng_val)          AS gwp_amt ,
            fact.rec_crt_dtm ,
            fact.rec_updt_dtm ,
            fact.actv_rec_ind ,
            fact.etl_audit_id ,
            fact.document_type ,
            fact.sales_type ,
            fact.valid_ind ,
            (fact.affects_direct_premium_amt * c.uf_lcl_curr_clsng_val) AS affects_direct_premium_amt ,
            (fact.exempt_direct_premium_amt * c.uf_lcl_curr_clsng_val ) AS exempt_direct_premium_amt,
            (fact.new_direct_premium_amt * c.uf_lcl_curr_clsng_val )    AS new_direct_premium_amt ,
            (fact.renewal_direct_premium_amt * c.uf_lcl_curr_clsng_val) AS renewal_direct_premium_amt,
            (fact.endorsement_direct_premium_amt * c.uf_lcl_curr_clsng_val ) AS endorsement_direct_premium_amt,
            fact.next_policy ,
            fact.previous_policy ,
            fact.item_renovated_ind ,
            fact.cycle_number ,
            fact.cycle_state ,
            fact.renovation_type ,
            fact.plate_number ,
            fact.insured_rut_num ,
            fact.policyholder_rut_num ,
            fact.Lob_mkt_ref_code ,
            fact.mv_id ,
            fact.mv_reason_cd ,
            fact.mv_reason_desc ,
            branch.branch_office_name ,
            broker.broker_name ,
            insured.insured_name ,
            lob.lob_desc ,
            policyholder.policyholder_name ,
            prd_pln.prd_desc ,
            broker.broker_rut_num,
            lob.lob_cd,
            prd_pln.pln_cd,
            insured.address_desc      AS address_desc_insured,
            insured.comuna_name       AS comuna_name_insured,
            insured.region_name       AS region_name_insured,
            policyholder.address_desc AS address_desc_policyholder,
            policyholder.comuna_name  AS comuna_name_policyholder,
            policyholder.region_name  AS region_name_policyholder,
            stg.ref_desc              AS coaseguro
        FROM
            cdp_dwh.fact_renovaciones_integrado_t_test fact
		left join (select sseguro,nmovimi,fmovimi as mv_dt from cdp_ods.sisaxis_movseguro) move_seg
        on fact.policy_item_id=cast(cast(move_seg.sseguro as integer) as varchar (35))
        and fact.mv_id=move_seg.nmovimi	
        LEFT JOIN
            ( select dim_branch_office_key,branch_office_name from  cdp_dwh.dim_branch_office_t ) branch
        ON fact.dim_branch_office_key=branch.dim_branch_office_key
        LEFT JOIN
            (select dim_broker_key,broker_name,broker_rut_num from cdp_dwh.dim_broker_t) broker
        ON fact.dim_broker_key=broker.dim_broker_key
        LEFT JOIN
            (select dim_insured_key,insured_name,address_desc,comuna_name,region_name from cdp_dwh.dim_insured_t) insured
        ON fact.dim_insured_key=insured.dim_insured_key
        LEFT JOIN
            (select dim_lob_key,lob_desc,lob_cd from cdp_dwh.dim_lob_t) lob
        ON fact.dim_lob_key=lob.dim_lob_key
        LEFT JOIN
            (select dim_policyholder_key,policyholder_name,address_desc,comuna_name,region_name from cdp_dwh.dim_policyholder_t) policyholder
        ON fact.dim_policyholder_key=policyholder.dim_policyholder_key
        LEFT JOIN
            (select dim_prd_pln_hrchy_key,prd_desc,pln_cd from cdp_dwh.dim_prd_pln_hrchy_t) prd_pln
        ON
            fact.dim_prd_pln_hrchy_key=prd_pln.dim_prd_pln_hrchy_key
        LEFT JOIN
            ( select uf_lcl_curr_clsng_val,curr_cd,vltn_dtm from cdp_dwh.curr_conv_t where curr_conv_frequency_cd = 'Daily' and src_sys_cd='axis') c
        ON
            fact.policy_curr_cd = c.curr_cd
        --AND fact.acct_mth= TO_CHAR(c.vltn_dtm,'MM')
        --AND fact.acct_yr = TO_CHAR(c.vltn_dtm,'YYYY')
        AND date(move_seg.mv_dt)=date(c.vltn_dtm)
        LEFT JOIN
            (select ref_cd,ref_desc from cdp_stg_dwh.stg_tref_code_map_variant 
            where ref_type_cd = 'cod_tipo_coaseguro' and src_sys_cd = 'axis')stg
        ON fact.coins_type_cd = stg.ref_cd
        
        WHERE fact.src_sys_cd='axis'
        AND fact.etl_audit_id='1'
         )
